# GCP Account Creation Issue

I encountered an issue while attempting to create a Google Cloud Platform (GCP) account. 
Despite trying two different payment cards, I was unable to complete the process. 
I kept receiving the following error: (Please see screenshot folder - GCP-CreditCard-Error.png).

As a workaround, I proceeded to create an Amazon EKS (Elastic Kubernetes Service) on AWS using Terraform. 
